build/

# note: web/ IS tracked in full — the v86 runtime + BIOS (web/vendor/) and the
# built disk image (web/os-image.bin, refreshed by `make web`) — so the browser
# demo is self-contained and deployable to GitHub Pages. Rebuild + `make web`
# then commit web/os-image.bin to update the live demo.
